  at 9 a.m.: House District 49 – Republican</li><li>Thursday\, June 25 at
  1 p.m.: House District 135 – Democrat  </li></ul><p>The recounts will
  take place in the Florian Room located at the Maine Public Safety Buildin
 g at 45 Commerce Ave.\, Augusta. Recounts are open to the public and media
  and will be livestreamed on the Secretary of State’s <a href="https://
 www.youtube.com/@mesecofstate">YouTube page</a>.</p><p>Additional recounts
  could be requested following the conclusion of the ranked choice voting t
 abulations.</p><p><strong>Recount process:</strong> Maine statute <a href
 ="https://legislature.maine.gov/legis/statutes/21-A/title21-Asec737-A.html
